================ README file for the JBA project =========================

JBA/BrainAligner project is for brain (and general 3D) image registration.

This project was started in Dec 2006 and Jan 2007, first in Matlab and from
Feb 2007 in C/C++. 

The program was written by Hanchuan Peng. All rights reserved.

To build the executable, simply go into jba sub-folder and type "make".

This folder also contains  a copy of the NEWMAT11 library, which is licensed
with its own terms. (http://www.robertnz.net/nm11x.htm)
